headline: Keefe Bruyette Maintains Market Perform on D.R. Horton, Inc. (DHI) While Trimming Price Target Amid Affordability and Incentive Pressures
summary: We recently published an article titled 10 Best Affordable Housing Stocks to Buy. On January 27, Keefe Bruyette lowered the firm’s price target on D.R. Horton, Inc. (NYSE:DHI) to $163 from $168 while maintaining a Market Perform rating on the shares, reflecting a more cautious outlook for the homebuilding sector amid affordability pressures and elevated […]
